                        <interp inst="t18420131-name-1190" type="surname" value="ABRAMS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420131-name-1190" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY ABRAMS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a potato-dealer—I live in King David-lane, Shadwell—the prisoner was my errand-boy. I sent out for 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. worth of silver on the 15th of January—I placed it on the mantel-piece in the back-parlour, two rooms from the shop—I went down stairs with the prisoner, and left my wife in the room—I sent the prisoner up to fetch some empty bas<lb></lb>kets—he did not return—I went up, and missed the silver off the mantel<lb></lb>piece—no one was in the place but the prisoner.</p>
